When creating a new user account on a clone PC:

Move into the /d/wokspaces/helios_workspace/gitscripts/ directory

Run "source refresh_bash_profile.sh"






If you are starting from scratch:

1. Download createRepo.sh into the directory you want to create the repo under

2. Enter the following in the shell wherever you downloaded that:

source createRepo.sh


3. Copy environment.sh.template to environment.sh and customize it

4. Run refresh_bash_profile.sh





